<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Horro Wolfrunner</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-06-22 16:22:56</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>There are actually 2 different librarians in Kaesora. One in human form and the other in the ghost form. The staff I received dropped off the human (tortured librarian) but had one significantly better stat than the stats show on this page. The staff seems to differ in weight. I have seen 2, one weighing 10 and the one I received only weighs 7.5, which makes a world of difference for a monk. </font></td></tr></table>
<BR>
<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Furyfist</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-06-26 08:31:27</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Got one last night in Keasora.  Mine dropped off the ghost librarian and weighs 7.5.  Its an easy dungeon to break and great xp for a group 35-40.  The librarians common drop is a 6 wis/int tome.  Also got a nifty weight reducing pack there.  8 slot, 20% weight reduction and only weighs 0.4.  </font></td></tr></table>
