<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I also got a staff, and am using it with mt lvl 13 monk twink, so far he hits way better with the staff than with his fists.  The torture librarian also gave us a few kunzar mantles and even 1 spirit tome.  We got 4 spirit tomes total that night, and over the course of 2 days I made about 10k...No one is ever in Kaesora so no one ever fights over spawns....It is the anti-guk.  Library also has a failed crypt keeper that drops a shaman weapon and a warder of xalgoz that drops a nice shadow knight weapon<BR>
