<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Nylan (Emarr)</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-09-01 02:38:47</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white><BR>
Just a quick note for the person who posted above -- <BR>
there are two melee damage caps, one at 10th and one <BR>
at 20th.  Until level 10, you can't hit for more than 20 <BR>
points, and until 20th you can't hit for more than 30 <BR>
regardless of the weapon.<BR>
<BR>
I may be off on the exact numbers, but the caps exist.  <BR>
<BR>
Our group pulled three of these out of 5 librarians a few<BR>
days ago, seems to be his more common drop.  Ours all came<BR>
from the ghost version of the librarian.</font></td></tr></table>
